trans-unit.source: Exposes <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> types to UI Automation.
trans-unit.target: Expone los tipos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> a la automatización de la interfaz de usuario.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Crea una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control type for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el tipo de control correspondiente al control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlType" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlType" /> llama a este método.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationControlType.Group" /> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: El valor de enumeración <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationControlType.Group" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of child elements of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> control that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />, and sets the event source of the templated toggle button to this <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la colección de elementos secundarios del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> que está asociado a este elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" /> y establece el origen de eventos del botón de alternancia con plantilla en esta instancia de <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore" />.

trans-unit.source: The collection of child elements of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> control associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Colección de elementos secundarios del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> asociado a este elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el nombre del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> asociado a esta clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClassName" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClassName" />.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains "Expander".
trans-unit.target: Cadena que contiene "Expander".

trans-unit.source: One of the enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: Uno de los valores de enumeración.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control pattern for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el patrón de control para <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: If <paramref name="pattern" /> is <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse" />, this method returns a reference to the current instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />, otherwise this method calls the base implementation on <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElementAutomationPeer" /> which returns <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Si <paramref name="pattern" /> es <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse" />, este método devuelve una referencia a la instancia actual de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ExpanderAutomationPeer" />; de lo contrario, este método llama a la implementación base en <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElementAutomationPeer" /> que devuelve <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the expander has automation keyboard focus.
trans-unit.target: Indica si el botón de expansión tiene el foco de teclado de automatización.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the expander has automation keyboard focus; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si el botón de expansión tiene el foco de teclado de automatización; en caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The expander should have automation keyboard focus whenever the actual focus is set in the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ToggleButton>.
trans-unit.target: El botón de expansión debe tener el foco del teclado de automatización siempre que el foco real se establece el <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ToggleButton>.
